Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個救世主而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲力…怎麼會消耗的這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個招數的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 到底是什麼個情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞 你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間內部發生劇烈的重力異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去會崩壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是因為打敗了文字怪獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快回收AQUARION 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.42,0:00:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左邊的口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遙遠的過去 人類曾與心理的世界共存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒過多久 文字帶來了繁榮與苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:13.93,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(662.4,457.601)}照亮吧 意志之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉呢 一直這麼混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡的還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿佐谷北高等學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年A組 灰吹陽君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來有很多事情需要和你講呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們需要我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該上鎖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且手銬也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 灰吹陽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們打算怎麼處置我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做出那種可怕的表情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:04:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是把你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們原來是會吃人類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管是炒還是醃漬都不會好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 剛才那是故意裝傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果覺得我礙事 殺了我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是被利用而妨礙到莊嚴大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不如被殺了好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不是那種可怕的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法理解莊嚴大人理想的愚蠢的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為有你們在！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會將人類從名為文字的束縛中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人與人之間真正互相理解的世界才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人所推崇的理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你們所謂的理想鄉從而犧牲的人們樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去想像過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了大義 有些犧牲是不可避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是叫莊嚴 莊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像動物的叫聲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有你搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就實現了莊嚴大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的聲音裡沒有你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有自己的意志 那就和人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在愚弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過後會由我來親自審問你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.49,0:05:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要老實說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想太暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次在現實聽到人說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個奪走Vector擅自出擊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不是什麼正經的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是個壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而 而且…敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打倒敵人也都多虧了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是將Vector當私物來用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 不愧是將來的議員大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦筋好死板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都輸了 根本沒資格說人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我發什麼火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你也太焦躁了 翼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是缺鈣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翔子 給他來點牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉 芒果果汁可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有 你也找個接近點的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是完全不同的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顏色上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 生氣了 最喜歡牛奶的翼人君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛 牛奶剛才被我喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心音 要是沒有牛奶 翼人在這個地球上連3分鐘都堅持不住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他是牛奶狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 這個明顯會悲劇的設定是什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛 牛奶狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我得去買點供奉在佛壇上的牛奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你不用哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要幫忙 叫我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了 救世主狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 發生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deava
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我們這個組織的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先向你說明一下我們的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從文字中誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬文字的怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稱之為 文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字的根源所居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.31,ps,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,670)}Logos World
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在理念世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變味文字怪獸的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其轉變的瞬間會創造出屬於自己的固有空間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並開始捕食在空間中飄蕩的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 文字的消失會影響到現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初 只是文字本身被侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 文字的意義所代表的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將在現實中強制發生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前幾日的文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從「卷」這個字中誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有很多東西被「卷」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有一些東西發生不能被「卷」的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字不分善惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字典裡的文字沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡意是透過人的意志與聲音得到力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而傷害他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定存在著一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包含著惡意操縱文字的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 的確有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過侵蝕存在虛無化的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而讓文字怪獸化的 我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社交網路服務運營公司NESTA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首席執行官 劍崎莊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 為什麼我們明明知道敵人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻還沒有去抓他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在還問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有不能對莊嚴直接出手的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算我們打敗了莊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有文字怪獸留下來 那也是我們的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字怪獸是絕對不會被消滅乾淨的癌細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當吞噬完自己的文字之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會衝進理念世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其他的文字也變成文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚一天 會吞噬掉所有的文字和概念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在變成那樣之前 能阻止那些傢伙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有能侵入敵人空間的Vector和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打倒文字怪獸唯一的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 能操縱AQUARION的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有創聲力的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只 只有我們創聲部才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰吹陽君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有著天下無雙的創聲力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入創聲部 和我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我會戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那麼想加入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然創聲部的活動 就如其名一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要做的可是拼上性命的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界遇到了危機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問為什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我就是 救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙挺有趣的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這麼容易就上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終究只是個外行自警團
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 我的Vector
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 全部解決掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個人數…要同時解決根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種完全統一的 沒有任何多餘動作的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是一流的軍隊也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個基地的最終防線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人衝過去就太無謀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能在這裡偷懶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰再用點力 腰這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明這麼年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能找機會偷偷溜進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你想別的去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是能看出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本毫無破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊拉 主任 感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是流行起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不能出擊啊 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎麼出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓Vector受損 落荒而逃的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是必須趕快去救舞亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒時間和你們折騰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回公司去 突然有了急事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你拿到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是營業時間你還是別拿出來比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你這是幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這種東西很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小心音又不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 翼人君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 心音因為家裡有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人是因為要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以說超忙的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翔子 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長 你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我必須去審問下那孩子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你過會再去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這裡有這麼多客人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力向前伸 向前用力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前伸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 沒有什麼污漬是擦不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出毅力來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 手腳俐落點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了這麼大的運動量的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能做出那種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然她們……不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 那我們吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了 便當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都有發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是丟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 正是發育身體的時候 那點怎麼夠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這個也給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勞動後的「白箱」便當相當不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我們也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.88,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz-7\fad(500,0)\pos(554,681)}身體以及量子文字現象研究中心別館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4個房間和與其連接的樓道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…我的世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所不知道的外面世界的人類們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正深陷於不幸之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 莊嚴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為被文字蔓延的世界囚禁住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才必須把文字從這個世界中驅逐出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是唯一的拯救方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沾上醬汁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要紙巾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那不是抹布嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…真的沒覺得這些人是不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情愉悅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我就將你解放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病~~~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會突然發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deava系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.39,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\frz-17\pos(425,598)}臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.36,post -blue,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(617,619)}真的十分抱歉 請下次再來光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救護班 加緊搬運病人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們聯絡一下急救中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經與翼人和小心音取得聯繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在往這邊趕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有很多人感冒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 應該就是虛無化所帶來的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 因為那個文字變成了文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受害範圍也就隨之變廣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 說起來救世主大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在無法出動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空筱機和土聞機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因為前日出擊的損傷過於巨大還在修理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是文字怪獸的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你們所謂的理想鄉從而犧牲的人們樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有去想像過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 你一個人又能怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 敵方那邊的可愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去做我應該做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 喂 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病…………
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊 霧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼做才好 莊嚴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後部推進裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平衡機能低下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要墜落進空間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰吹君 暫時先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人和人之間做到真正互相理解的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會傷害人的文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不過是為了莊嚴大人的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是那樣 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不想再看到那些人痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？好大的口氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個 就是你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上 借我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲合體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心和身是一體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要心靈健康
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體就能保持健全的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百病由氣而生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明 一起照亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 開始下午的工作了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有時間休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小心音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有小心音在 我們就能精神一萬倍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰吹陽 是那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音呼喚回了文字的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光明將黑暗驅除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然他就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被創聲之力所選中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到莊嚴大人那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:21:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 舞亞在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正要回到莊嚴大人那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就留在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去監視紅色Vector駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我們三個女孩子來擔任解說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長早不是女孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:23:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時薪降低50圓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就從「白箱」辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你便 那我就讓小心音來打工
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努 努 努力當上店長的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.43,0:24:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的上進心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 第三話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,響徹吧 屬於我的夢想
